         = 0.197649

P(X = 8) = $\binom{8}{8}(0.70)^8(0.30)^0$
         = 1 × (0.70)^8 × 1
         = 0.05764801

P(Y₇ < 27.3) = 0.197649 + 0.05764801
              = 0.25529701
              ≈ 0.2553

