**Finding P(Xᵢ ≥ 9) for a single drug:**

P(X = k) = C(10,k) × 0.7^k × 0.3^(10-k)

P(X = 9) = C(10,9) × 0.7⁹ × 0.3¹
= 10 × 0.040353607 × 0.3
= 0.121060821

P(X = 10) = C(10,10) × 0.7¹⁰ × 0.3⁰
= 1 × 0.0282475249 × 1
= 0.0282475249

